descriptionHtml:
[size=4]  Due to a request i will be releasing my character preset for the dark elf i posted awhile back[/size]
[size=4]  You will notice it comes in two parts.

[/size]
[size=5]  [/size][size=5]Requirements[/size]
   (If you want her to look exact)
[list=1]
[*][size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RACEMENU[/url] by expired6978[/size]
[*][size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/58989/?]Citrus Heads[/url] by blabba[/size]
[*][size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]Eyes Of Beauty[/url] by LoGraam[/size]
[*][size=3][url=http://iamthekingofsass.tumblr.com/post/113280875138/ladies-and-peens-here-it-is-smashin-face]Smashin Face Overhaul[/url] by KingOfSass (OPTIONAL but mind you she will look different due to different textures)[/size]
[*][size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70363/?]KS Hairdos HDT[/url] by Stealthic and Kalilies (OPTIONAL) [/size]
[/list]

[size=5]  [u]Instructions
[/u][/size]
[list=1]
[*]Drag all files to correct location.
[/list] (Steam.../Skyrim/Data/SKSE/Plugins)
        (nif file goes into CharGen folder)
(slot file goes into presets folder)

    2. When in game make sure to select the Dark elf race
   
    3. Make sure to apply the head mesh first
    
    4. Then apply preset and tweak her to your liking



    [u][size=5]NOTICE

[/size][/u]    She does have a neck seam in the back of the neck which is what i will be working on to fix at the moment
author: Fopbomb aka Voltyx
